@lambos2k  A few things, the free Acrobat Reader is not the same as Acrobat pro. If you have trouble with any of the installed Adobe applications my recommendation is to remove all traces of all installed Adobe software and install CS5 and Acrobat again. See the re-post by st16121 above for instructions.

To get Acrobat 9 pro (not included in the CS5 torrent) Google "Acrobat 9 pro mac torrent" and the top link is actually from The Piratebay. There are many alternative torrent sites (e.g. btjunkie) and again Google is your friend for finding them.

After installing Acrobat 9 run Adobe Acrobat > Help > Check for Updates? multiple times until Adobe Acrobat 9 Pro is up to date (version 9.3.2 at the date of this post).

